Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:35.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Veil of Shadows]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:38.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Episode 1]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:29.85,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Why's someone lying there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:30.47,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:33.50,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Seventh day of the tenth month]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:40.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Someone's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:41.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Someone's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[The Well-Woven House]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:55.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,they found another body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:56.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.54,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Fourteenth day of the tenth month]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.45,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Again, his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.63,0:03:02.68,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,was ripped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I heard a high-rank demon's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:07.45,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So we can't stay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,in Luo'an anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Now the whole town's in panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:11.89,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,That demon will surely
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:12.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,keep killing and taking hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Who knows who'll be next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Twenty-first day of the tenth month]\NHow terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:18.26,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,To keep their wedding going,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the Wei family specially hired
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,a demon hunter from the Shilin Sect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- This isn't just any demon hunter, - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- That's it! - but someone with a flower on his forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:24.78,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Miss, you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:36.78,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm the Wei family's bride-to-be's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:46.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:47.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,My name's Yu Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:50.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Please, follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.08,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Wei Qing, head of the Wei family]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:03:59.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Here, Shengwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.59,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Yu Shengwei, daughter of the Yu family]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.50,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.24,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Luo Wei, steward of the Wei mansion]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The wedding dress will be done in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'll deliver it to the Yu mansion myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Guess we should go pray at the Dragon Deity Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.75,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,May we stay deeply in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and grow old together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:20.54,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:22.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Come on, Wei Qing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.75,0:04:29.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Deity doesn't handle that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.43,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Liu Weixue, Wei Qing's cousin]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Miss Yu's cousin has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Shengwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I know it's been a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.85,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,but you really don't recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm your cousin,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:55.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Yu Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:01.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:04.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're Yu Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:15.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Twenty-fourth day of the tenth month]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:07.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I've got a hostage now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.62,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Dare you chase me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.50,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Ow, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.50,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What kind of weirdo are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:44.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Why'd you hang me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:45.62,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Untie me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You demon hunters are something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Go after that greater fox demon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,that's been killing and stealing hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:51.62,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Why come after me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:53.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,an innocent little weasel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:54.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,No, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:12.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Thank you, kind sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.96,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,for saving my life a second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,No problem, Miss Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:17.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Second time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wei's arranged
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:26.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,a dinner banquet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to thank you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Please rest here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:32.81,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Wu Shiguang]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:47.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:49.44,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[You Chi, low-rank weasel demon]\NDid I nail my act?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,All thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.39,0:07:51.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to my majestic black smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.02,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Absolutely brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:57.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Half a month ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.54,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,a broken-tail fox attacked Miss Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.41,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It must be linked to the heart-stealing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:03.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:06.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,those arrogant demon hunters from the Shilin Sect
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,wouldn't have been guards
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,for an ordinary family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.23,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Yu told me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,how you were kind enough
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to save her half a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:47.15,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,She could've died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:56.89,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,But that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,it was really dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.84,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Half a month ago]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.37,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:03.92,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Seventh day of the tenth month]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:04.50,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.26,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:24.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Eight tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:26.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,A broken-tail fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.51,0:09:29.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.20,0:09:40.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,That fox demon moves without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.65,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Really terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Shengwei,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:50.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,have your favorite chestnut cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:51.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It may comfort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:58.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wu, you're truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't chased that fox demon off,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:02.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,my cousin's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,would've been ripped out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I didn't exactly chase it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:07.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,And that day marked
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:08.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the first murder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,in this whole heart-stealing case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:11.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,That broken-tail fox
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,must be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It might've been hiding in this mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:17.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,so it will try again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to harm Miss Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:23.85,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The air above this estate is thick with demonic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I fear a high-rank demon has taken root here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wei,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,if you're willing to hire me as a house guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.37,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I can definitely protect Miss Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:41.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Although Master Wu is just a wandering hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,with no real background,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:49.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,although
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,he couldn't actually defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the fox demon last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:52.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,although
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,he probably still doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,where the fox demon is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,or how to guard against it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.65,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,although no one knows
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,if he could win if it does show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:05.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,one thing's sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:10.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,he's so handsome,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,with such a great build.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Having him stay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,by my cousin's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Shengwei will surely be "safe."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a sure thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,but Wei Qing's got such a small mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:47.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:48.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,who really wants us gone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:50.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,isn't Wei Qing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,but this cousin of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.03,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Rucui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Is it time yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:41.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Rucui?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:02.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:03.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,are we sure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:04.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,this isn't dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The heart thefts started on Oct 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:09.37,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Every seven days, someone dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:10.81,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Today,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.23,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the fox demon should strike again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Nothing ventured, nothing gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.33,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,If you want to catch the heart-stealing demon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.62,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and claim the bounty from the Shilin Sect,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,then shut up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So the fox demon wanted to kill Miss Yu that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:25.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,but failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,so it killed someone else instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:29.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Then every seven days after,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:30.26,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,it kills one person on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.69,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm just too smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.65,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:49.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Twenty-eighth day of the tenth month, auspicious for weddings]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.11,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.40,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[The Well-Woven House]\NCongrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:17.92,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Please, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:18.59,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:20.84,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Just put it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:21.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.03,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Come, this way please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:26.26,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What a perfect day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:27.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.20,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Come on, right inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.03,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Ji Ling]\NThe nine-tailed fox's magic is right in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Li Jie]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:47.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:48.85,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:51.79,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:52.44,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[The Well-Woven House]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.04,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Please, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.15,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- Come on in! - This way, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- No need for formalities. - Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:02.08,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.03,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- Congrats! - Right this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:04.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:06.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,it's crowded and busy inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:07.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Please leave your names
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and your wedding gifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,so I can record them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:13.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Well, the gifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.37,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The gifts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:16.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Li Jie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:23.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:30.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,All these human customs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,are such a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:34.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,This door's flimsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:36.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I could smash it with one swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:40.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.32,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[The Well-Woven House]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:47.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Oh, Master Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Your presence honors our humble home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Madame Zhao,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:54.80,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,you've arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.83,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Come in, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're not Miss Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Miss Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:18.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,doesn't have a vixen face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,And you're not Master Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Master Wei
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:25.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,wouldn't hold a knife to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:31.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're so eager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.33,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,They say
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:38.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the first night together is priceless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,How could I not be eager?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.11,0:18:43.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Since we're now wed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,we should be open with each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:54.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,my husband would have two faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:00.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Too bad
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,one woman shouldn't serve two husbands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:05.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So, how about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,you let me down first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Well then, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,you'll have to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,take that dagger away from me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:30.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Trying to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:10.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Such a beautiful vase,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:12.33,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and you have no taste for elegance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.33,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Someone as beautiful as me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:15.86,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and you have no taste either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I'm divorcing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:28.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Pretty clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:33.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Steward Luo of this family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Why is she sneaking around
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:35.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,in her own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:37.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.03,0:22:15.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:18.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Her accomplices?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:39.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Why are you stopping me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.79,0:22:41.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You reek of demonic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:43.45,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're a fox demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:46.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,She's that heart-eating demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:50.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Heaven really is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It gives you such a handsome face,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:55.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,but no brains to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:11.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Groom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:14.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,why the sudden change of your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.63,0:23:16.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Your opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:17.89,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.51,0:24:21.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You have no sacred power?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:22.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Does that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.28,0:24:24.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,stop me from fighting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.91,0:25:28.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Who exactly are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.11,0:25:29.85,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.03,0:25:31.50,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.11,0:25:34.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm the demon hunter Wu Shiguang.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.08,0:25:36.85,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Since when do demon hunters
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:38.31,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,have to worry about so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.76,0:25:39.78,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,even playing the groom?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.16,0:25:41.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm pretending to be the groom
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.11,0:25:43.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,for one reason only...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.08,0:25:45.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to catch a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.03,0:25:50.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.28,0:25:52.41,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,We're demon hunters too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.79,0:25:53.89,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,We're also here to catch demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.99,0:25:56.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,But unlike you back-alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.11,0:25:57.41,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,rogue demon hunters,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.60,0:25:59.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,we're official demon hunters from the Shilin Sect,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.52,0:26:01.41,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,sent here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:03.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to investigate the heart-stealing case.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.55,0:26:04.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,This is the Shilin Sect's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.60,0:26:05.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,demon hunter commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.40,0:26:06.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Li Jie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.72,0:26:10.33,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Stunned now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.16,0:26:34.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,An ice-wielding demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.52,0:26:36.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Sure enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.91,0:26:38.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,you're the one we're after!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.87,0:26:40.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What grudge do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.91,0:26:42.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I don't even know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.43,0:26:45.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Trying to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.40,0:27:20.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:27.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.55,0:27:29.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.20,0:27:36.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Let... let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.31,0:27:39.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.75,0:27:40.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.16,0:27:43.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.92,0:27:53.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Still trying to flee?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.68,0:28:38.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir, for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.79,0:28:41.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.16,0:28:43.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're thanking the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.44,0:28:44.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The groom saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.55,0:28:45.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Thank him instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.42,0:28:51.89,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Thank you, kind sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.75,0:28:53.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.79,0:28:55.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What are those red threads
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.00,0:28:56.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.68,0:29:01.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.92,0:29:02.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,it's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.24,0:29:05.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Submit now,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.75,0:29:06.86,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,or die trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.07,0:29:08.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.11,0:29:11.81,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Do I look like I'm struggling?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.88,0:29:13.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm a demon hunter too,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.51,0:29:15.62,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,here to catch demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.11,0:29:17.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What crime have I committed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.16,0:29:17.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.24,0:29:20.62,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Now the whole room's full of demon hunters,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.64,0:29:21.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.72,0:29:23.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Don't count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.31,0:29:26.67,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm no demon hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.03,0:29:28.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm a respectable woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.51,0:29:30.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Don't bother denying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.51,0:29:31.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,We traced the demonic energy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.48,0:29:32.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.59,0:29:34.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're the nine-tailed fox stealing hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.07,0:29:41.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,How terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.96,0:29:43.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.24,0:29:45.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,was she trying to rip out my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.75,0:29:48.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.11,0:29:50.33,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,A heart-eating demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.64,0:29:53.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Are you joking,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:54.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,or serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.10,0:29:56.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- I... - Who has time
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.07,0:29:57.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to joke with a fox demon like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.40,0:30:01.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're the sect's demon hunter commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.03,0:30:03.86,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.96,0:30:06.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What's your identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.48,0:30:09.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.16,0:30:16.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.59,0:30:18.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What should I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.67,0:30:19.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,My name is Ji Ling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.72,0:30:20.69,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Ji means "life's a journey,"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.75,0:30:21.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and Ling means "hearts that beat as one."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.83,0:30:22.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Stay here,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.48,0:30:23.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and don't run off, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.20,0:30:25.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.59,0:30:28.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.96,0:30:30.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,This female demon is really terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.72,0:30:32.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.92,0:30:33.73,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.83,0:30:35.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.11,0:30:41.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.10,0:31:09.58,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Li Mao, wedding guest of the Wei family]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.70,0:31:15.78,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Tao Xi, Li Mao's wife]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.00,0:31:34.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Weimiao Pavilion...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.44,0:31:44.86,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.20,0:32:15.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It's frost.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.35,0:32:22.14,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It's not even winter yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.07,0:32:24.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Why is there all this frost?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.51,0:32:27.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It's demon magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.36,0:32:39.74,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Those prayer beads are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.64,0:32:41.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What's their story?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.43,0:32:48.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Don't touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.19,0:32:51.74,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Keep them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.75,0:32:54.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You're so thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.59,0:32:55.33,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.35,0:32:57.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,And you're so clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.88,0:32:59.25,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you tipping me off,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.00,0:33:01.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I was able to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.79,0:33:05.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Wangyan,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.59,0:33:07.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the groom's a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.59,0:33:09.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,He's here to catch fox demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.88,0:33:12.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.24,0:33:14.36,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Don't let him
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.24,0:33:16.45,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,make it real,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.59,0:33:17.81,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,or turn the tables on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.72,0:33:21.29,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd guarded against one,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.51,0:33:22.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and now two more show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.96,0:33:25.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,That Ji Ling guy
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.55,0:33:28.81,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and his long-blade friend
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.59,0:33:30.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,won't be easy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.20,0:33:34.77,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,But the one really hard to shake
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.31,0:33:36.86,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,is that guy who won't let me go,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.96,0:33:38.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Wu Shiguang.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.31,0:33:40.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.79,0:33:43.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.11,0:33:46.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Wangyan,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.59,0:33:48.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,want to make a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.07,0:35:38.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Broken-tail fox,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.36,0:35:41.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,it really is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.51,0:36:32.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Miss Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.80,0:36:36.93,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I asked you to gather some intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:38.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Did you get it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.96,0:36:39.74,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.32,0:36:42.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,There are 952 weasels in Luo'an City.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.55,0:36:43.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,From street gossip
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.48,0:36:44.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to corner rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.55,0:36:45.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,they know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.76,0:36:46.92,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the bride,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.92,0:36:47.69,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Miss Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.92,0:36:49.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,She's Luo'an's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.11,0:36:50.16,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,famous embroiderer,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.40,0:36:51.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,especially skilled
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.76,0:36:52.78,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,at stitching birds and beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.07,0:36:56.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Now, Luo Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.40,0:36:58.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,This woman's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.67,0:37:00.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,A month ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.59,0:37:02.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the Wei family's business faced a crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.32,0:37:03.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,almost went bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.63,0:37:05.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Then Luo Wei appeared out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.36,0:37:06.26,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and turned things around.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.07,0:37:08.16,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,After that, she joined the Wei mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.23,0:37:09.07,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and became the steward.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.36,0:37:10.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Everyone in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.19,0:37:11.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,fears and respects her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.76,0:37:12.65,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,And gossip says
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.00,0:37:14.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,she's got a thing for Wei Qing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.36,0:37:14.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.23,0:37:16.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,she really dislikes Miss Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.40,0:37:23.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,As for Liu Weixue,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.88,0:37:25.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,he's Wei Qing's distant cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.15,0:37:27.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,The Liu family's been generals for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.67,0:37:28.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,But despite all his skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.67,0:37:30.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Liu Weixue refuses
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.23,0:37:31.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to go to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.20,0:37:33.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- Half a month ago, - Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.27,0:37:35.02,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,he fled an arranged marriage and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.23,0:37:36.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,- Bring the wine! - Word on the street is
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:37.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,he might be interested in Luo Wei.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.19,0:37:39.39,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Quick, bring the medicine wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.28,0:37:41.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.23,0:37:43.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So lively late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.36,0:37:45.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,And Yu Wei
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.48,0:37:46.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,grew up in the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.84,0:37:47.69,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,not from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.19,0:37:49.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Their families
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.44,0:37:50.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,rarely interact.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.00,0:37:52.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So her showing up for the feast
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.36,0:37:54.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,is pretty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.03,0:37:59.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Oh, quite a crowd here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.92,0:38:04.74,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Miss Yu Wei!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.67,0:38:06.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Weren't you supposed to stay in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.15,0:38:08.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.84,0:38:09.94,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,It's so dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.55,0:38:14.26,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Since you called her a demon,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.07,0:38:16.11,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,how could I stay
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.11,0:38:17.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,in the same room with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.71,0:38:19.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Plus,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:22.05,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,she totally wrecked my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.67,0:38:24.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So I came here
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.80,0:38:25.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to change into new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.40,0:38:29.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,So, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.36,0:38:32.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,do I look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.80,0:38:36.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Yeah... good.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.55,0:38:39.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.55,0:38:42.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Where's the bride I tied up?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.32,0:38:44.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.23,0:38:46.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,are you looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.84,0:38:57.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I followed the broken-tail fox here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.15,0:38:59.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,But the moment I entered this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.44,0:39:01.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,it vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.11,0:39:04.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.59,0:39:06.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.67,0:39:08.86,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,among all of you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.48,0:39:11.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.36,0:39:14.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,is the heart-stealing killer I'm after,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.19,0:39:17.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,the broken-tail fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.06,0:39:30.07,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[The runaway fox's hiding in the Wei mansion]
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.07,0:39:30.86,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Wu Wangyan,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.63,0:39:33.17,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,proceed to Luo'an at once
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.00,0:39:35.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,and bring Xiaowei back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.15,0:39:37.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.88,0:39:40.57,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.28,0:39:42.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,My mission
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.44,0:39:43.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,is still to assist her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.44,0:39:45.26,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Your mission
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.92,0:39:47.13,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,is to get close
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.40,0:39:49.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,to a young man named Ji Ling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.88,0:39:51.49,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,He is your fated one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.00,0:39:53.65,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Fated one?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.07,0:39:56.69,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Wangyan,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.36,0:39:58.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,what does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.84,0:40:03.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.11,0:40:05.01,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,All five of you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:06.53,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,are suspects!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.32,0:40:08.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,And you two
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.76,0:40:10.61,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,are no simple cases either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.84,0:40:16.78,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Bai Ze has brought news
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.92,0:40:18.21,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,of the nine-tailed fox, Xiaowei.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.21,0:40:19.28,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,[Shilin Sect, Scale Cave]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.28,0:40:20.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Right now, she's hiding in the Wei mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.44,0:40:22.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,in Luo'an.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.59,0:40:25.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Li Jie,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.32,0:40:28.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,it's time to bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.48,0:40:30.09,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.50,0:41:37.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪It's your light♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.86,0:41:39.74,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.90,0:41:43.02,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪That set the night alight♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.38,0:41:49.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪And lead me through the fight♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.66,0:41:53.54,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.98,0:41:58.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.22,0:42:00.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.06,0:42:06.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.22,0:42:12.62,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.94,0:42:20.98,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.94,0:42:24.10,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.38,0:42:29.22,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.58,0:42:31.90,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.10,0:42:37.18,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.42,0:42:39.42,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.70,0:42:44.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.06,0:42:52.02,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.58,0:43:11.54,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.62,0:43:16.02,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.82,0:43:19.34,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.58,0:43:22.66,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.06,0:43:25.38,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Let every dream and wild desire♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.90,0:43:30.30,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.54,0:43:32.70,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.10,0:43:38.06,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.30,0:43:39.46,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪It's your light♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.66,0:43:41.50,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.70,0:43:44.82,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪That set the night alight♪
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.58,0:43:55.02,优酷剧集英语,,0,0,0,,♪And lead me sailing afar♪
